# SSH Config

Host *
    ServerAliveInterval 60
    ServerAliveCountMax 30
    AddKeysToAgent yes
    IdentitiesOnly yes
    HashKnownHosts yes
    Compression yes

# GitHub
Host github.com
    User git
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_github
    ControlMaster auto
    ControlPath ~/.ssh/sockets/%r@%h:%p
    ControlPersist 600

